<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="th">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>500 - เกิดข้อผิดพลาด</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
  <style>
    .error-container {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      min-height: 100vh;
      background: #1E1F22;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .error-content {
      text-align: center;
      max-width: 600px;
      padding: 40px;
      background: #2B2D31;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
    }

    .error-icon {
      width: 120px;
      height: 120px;
      margin: 0 auto 24px;
      color: #F23F43;
    }

    .error-title {
      font-size: 48px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #F2F3F5;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .error-subtitle {
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #F2F3F5;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .error-description {
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #949BA4;
      margin-bottom: 32px;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .error-actions {
      display: flex;
      gap: 12px;
      justify-content: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .error-button {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      background: #5865F2;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 4px;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 500;
      transition: all 0.2s;
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    .error-button:hover {
      background: #4752C4;
      transform: translateY(-1px);
    }

    .error-button.secondary {
      background: #4E5058;
    }

    .error-button.secondary:hover {
      background: #5D5F66;
    }

    .error-code {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #80848E;
      margin-top: 24px;
      font-family: 'Consolas', 'Monaco', monospace;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .error-content {
        padding: 24px;
      }

      .error-title {
        font-size: 36px;
      }

      .error-subtitle {
        font-size: 18px;
      }

      .error-icon {
        width: 80px;
        height: 80px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="error-container">
    <div class="error-content">
      <div class="error-icon">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
          <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle>
          <line x1="15" y1="9" x2="9" y2="15"></line>
          <line x1="9" y1="9" x2="15" y2="15"></line>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h1 class="error-title">500</h1>
      <h2 class="error-subtitle">เกิดข้อผิดพลาดภายในเซิร์ฟเวอร์</h2>
      <p class="error-description">
        มีบางอย่างผิดพลาดในระบบ<br>
        กรุณาลองใหม่อีกครั้งในภายหลัง
      </p>
      <div class="error-actions">
        <a href="/" class="error-button">
          <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M3 9l9-7 9 7v11a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2z"></path>
            <polyline points="9 22 9 12 15 12 15 22"></polyline>
          </svg>
          กลับหน้าหลัก
        </a>
        <button class="error-button secondary" onclick="window.location.reload()">
          <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <polyline points="23 4 23 10 17 10"></polyline>
            <polyline points="1 20 1 14 7 14"></polyline>
            <path d="M3.51 9a9 9 0 0 1 14.85-3.36L23 10M1 14l4.64 4.36A9 9 0 0 0 20.49 15"></path>
          </svg>
          โหลดใหม่
        </button>
      </div>
      <div class="error-code">
        Error Code: 500 | Internal Server Error
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>

